const Months = Object.freeze({
    "January" : "Leden",
    "February" : "Únor",
    "March" : "Březen",
    "April" : "Duben",
    "May" : "Květen",
    "June" : "Červen",
    "July" : "Červenec",
    "August" : "Srpen",
    "September" : "Září",
    "October" : "Říjen",
    "November" : "Listopad",
    "December" : "Prosinec",
});

export default Months;
